		</span></span></div><div class="foswikiContentHeader"></div><div class="patternContent"><div class="foswikiTopic"><h1 id="GridLayoutPlugin">  <a class="foswikiCurrentTopicLink" href="/bin/view/System/GridLayoutPlugin">GridLayoutPlugin</a> </h1>
A 12er grid system for responsive layouts
<p></p>

<div class="foswikiToc" id="foswikiTOC"><span class="foswikiTocTitle">On this page:</span> <ul>
<li> <a href="?sortcol=4;table=6;up=0#Description"> Description </a>
